metadata.name: The New Icon - BALENCIAGA
metadata.description:
What does brands mean to you?

Have you ever met a person, who wants to be someone except himself? The power of brands in social media is insane. Brands are the new icons in our world. You see them, you want them. But there is the only one person, who make them powerful and that is you. Can you save your consciousness in a rush for brands and acceptance in social media? Simple things - big impact.
